<text><body>
<lb n="1118c05" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="1118c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c07" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 396</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="1118c08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說法滅盡經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="1118c09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="1118060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（僧祐…錄））十三字＝（（僧祐錄失譯））五字【宋】【宮】，（（僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄））十一字【元】【明】</note><app n="1118060" cb:word-count="13"><lem wit="【大】">僧祐錄中失譯經人名今附宋錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">僧祐錄失譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="1118c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1101">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1104" rend="inline">一時佛在拘夷那竭國——如來三月當
<lb n="1118c12" ed="T"/>般涅槃——與諸比丘及諸菩薩。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1212" rend="inline">無央數眾來詣
<lb n="1118c13" ed="T"/><note n="1118061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛所＝如來【宮】</note><app n="1118061"><lem wit="【大】">佛所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">如來</rdg></app>，稽首于<note n="1118062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地＋（眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法）【元】【明】</note><app n="1118062"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">地眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法</rdg></app>。世尊寂靜默無所說，光明
<lb n="1118c14" ed="T"/>不現。賢者阿難作禮白佛言：「<note n="1118063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世尊〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118063"><lem wit="【大】">世尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>前後說
<lb n="1118c15" ed="T"/>法威光獨顯，今大眾會光更不現，何故如此？
<lb n="1118c16" ed="T"/><note n="1118064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其必有＝必有緣【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其必有＝必有緣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118064"><lem wit="【大】">其必有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">必有緣</rdg></app>故，願聞其意。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1609" rend="inline">佛默不應，如是至三。</p>
<lb n="1118c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1701">佛告阿難：「吾涅槃後法欲滅時，五逆濁世魔
<lb n="1118c18" ed="T"/>道興盛。魔作沙門壞亂吾道，著俗衣裳，樂好
<lb n="1118c19" ed="T"/>袈裟、五色之服；飲酒、噉肉、殺生、貪味；無有
<lb n="1118c20" ed="T"/>慈心，更相憎嫉。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c2007" rend="inline">「時有菩薩、辟支、羅漢，精進修
<pb n="1119a" xml:id="T12.0396.1119a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1119a01" ed="T"/>德，一切敬待，人所宗向教化平等——憐貧、念老、
<lb n="1119a02" ed="T"/><note n="1119001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鞠＝救【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鞠＝救【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119001"><lem wit="【大】">鞠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">救</rdg></app>育窮厄。恒以經像令人奉事，作諸功德；志
<lb n="1119a03" ed="T"/>性<note n="1119002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恩＝思【元】【明】</note><app n="1119002"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">思</rdg></app>善，不侵害人；<note n="1119003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捐＝損【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捐＝損【宋】【宮】【麗-CB】【CB】</note><app n="1119003"><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">損<note type="cf1">K14n0520_p0056a17</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">捐</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">損</rdg></app>身濟物，不自惜己，忍
<lb n="1119a04" ed="T"/>辱仁和。設有是人，眾魔比丘咸共<note n="1119004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嫉＝疾【宮】</note><app n="1119004"><lem wit="【大】">嫉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">疾</rdg></app>之，誹謗
<lb n="1119a05" ed="T"/>揚惡，擯黜驅遣不令得住。自共於後不修道
<lb n="1119a06" ed="T"/>德，寺廟空荒無復修理轉就毀壞；但貪財物，
<lb n="1119a07" ed="T"/>積聚不散，不作福德；販賣奴婢耕田種植、焚
<lb n="1119a08" ed="T"/>燒山林、傷害眾生，無有慈心。奴為比丘、婢為
<lb n="1119a09" ed="T"/>比丘尼，無有道德，<note n="1119005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬妷＝淫泆【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1119005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬妷＝淫泆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1119005"><lem wit="【大】">婬妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">淫泆</rdg></app>濁亂，男女不別，令道
<lb n="1119a10" ed="T"/>薄淡皆由斯輩。或避縣官依倚吾道，求作沙
<lb n="1119a11" ed="T"/>門，不修戒律。月半月盡<note n="1119006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雖＝假【宮】</note><app n="1119006"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">假</rdg></app>名<note n="1119007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝講【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119007"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">講</rdg></app>戒，厭倦懈
<lb n="1119a12" ed="T"/>怠不欲聽聞，<note n="1119008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔抄略前後不肯盡說〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119008"><lem wit="【大】">抄略前後不肯盡說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。經不誦習，
<lb n="1119a13" ed="T"/>設有讀者不識字句，為強言是。不諮明者貢
<lb n="1119a14" ed="T"/>高求名，虛顯雅步以為榮冀，望人供養。眾魔
<lb n="1119a15" ed="T"/>比丘命終之後，精神當墮無<note n="1119009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擇＝澤【宋】</note><app n="1119009"><lem wit="【大】">擇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">澤</rdg></app>地獄，五逆
<lb n="1119a16" ed="T"/>罪中餓鬼、畜生靡不經歷，恒河沙劫罪竟<note n="1119010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝能【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119010"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">能</rdg></app>
<lb n="1119a17" ed="T"/>出，生在邊國無三寶處。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119a1710" rend="inline">「法欲滅時，女人精進，
<lb n="1119a18" ed="T"/>恒作<note n="1119011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">功＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">功＝福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119011"><lem wit="【大】">功</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>德；男子懈慢，不用法語，眼見沙門如
<lb n="1119a19" ed="T"/>視糞土，無有信心。法將殄沒，登爾之時諸天
<lb n="1119a20" ed="T"/>泣淚。水旱不調、五穀不熟，<note n="1119012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔疫氣流行死亡者眾〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119012"><lem wit="【大】">疫氣流行死亡者
<lb n="1119a21" ed="T"/>眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。人民勤苦，縣官<note n="1119013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">計剋＝剋罰【元】【明】</note><app n="1119013"><lem wit="【大】">計剋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">剋罰</rdg></app>，不順道理，皆思樂
<lb n="1119a22" ed="T"/>亂。惡人轉多如海中沙，善者甚少若一、若二。
<lb n="1119a23" ed="T"/>劫欲盡<note n="1119014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故＝處【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故＝處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119014"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">處</rdg></app>，日月轉<note n="1119015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">短＝促【元】【明】</note><app n="1119015"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">促</rdg></app>、人命轉<note n="1119016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">促＝短【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">促＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119016"><lem wit="【大】">促</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">短</rdg></app>。四十頭白，
<lb n="1119a24" ed="T"/>男子<app type="star" corresp="#1119005"><lem wit="【大】">婬妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">淫泆</rdg></app>，精盡夭命，或壽六十。男子壽短，女
<lb n="1119a25" ed="T"/>人壽長，七、<note n="1119017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＝十【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八＝十【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119017"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">十</rdg></app>、九十或至百歲。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119a2512" rend="inline">「大水忽起卒至
<lb n="1119a26" ed="T"/>無期，世人不信故為有常。眾生、雜類，<note n="1119018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不問＝無有【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不問＝無有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119018"><lem wit="【大】">不問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">無有</rdg></app>
<lb n="1119a27" ed="T"/><note n="1119019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">豪＝高【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119019"><lem wit="【大】">豪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">高</rdg></app>賤，沒溺<note n="1119020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">浮漂＝流飄【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浮漂＝流飄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119020"><lem wit="【大】">浮漂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">流飄</rdg></app>，魚鱉食噉。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119a2711" rend="inline">「<note n="1119021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時有〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119021"><lem wit="【大】">時有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩、辟支、
<lb n="1119a28" ed="T"/>羅漢，眾魔驅逐不<note n="1119022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">預＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">預＝與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119022"><lem wit="【大】">預</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">與</rdg></app>眾會。三乘入山福德之
<lb n="1119a29" ed="T"/>地，恬<note n="1119023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怕＝泊【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1119023"><lem wit="【大】">怕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">泊</rdg></app>自守以為欣快，<note n="1119024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔壽命延長〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119024"><lem wit="【大】">壽命延長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。諸<note n="1119025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝王【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天＝王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119025"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">王</rdg></app>衛
<pb n="1119b" xml:id="T12.0396.1119b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1119b01" ed="T"/>護月光出世，得相遭值，共興<note n="1119026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾＝五【宮】</note><app n="1119026"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">五</rdg></app>道五十二
<lb n="1119b02" ed="T"/>歲。《首楞嚴經》、《般舟三昧》先化滅去，十二部經
<lb n="1119b03" ed="T"/><note n="1119027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尋＝尊【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119027"><lem wit="【大】">尋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">尊</rdg></app>後
<note n="1119028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（復滅…文字））十字＝（（化滅聖王去後））六字【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（復滅…文字））十字＝（（化滅聖王去後））六字【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119028" cb:word-count="10"><lem wit="【大】">復滅，盡不復現。不見文字</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化滅聖王去後</rdg></app>，沙門袈裟
<lb n="1119b04" ed="T"/>自然變白。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119b0405" rend="inline">「吾法滅時，譬如油燈，臨欲滅時光
<lb n="1119b05" ed="T"/><note n="1119029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明更盛於是便滅＝更明盛【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明更盛於是便滅＝更明盛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119029"><lem wit="【大】">明更盛，於是便滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">更明盛</rdg></app>；吾法滅時亦如燈滅。自
<lb n="1119b06" ed="T"/>此之後難可數說。如是<note n="1119030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝又【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119030"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">又</rdg></app>後數千萬歲，彌勒
<lb n="1119b07" ed="T"/>當下世間作佛，天下泰平，毒氣消除，雨潤和
<lb n="1119b08" ed="T"/>適，五穀滋茂。樹木長大、人長八丈，皆壽八萬
<lb n="1119b09" ed="T"/>四千歲，眾生得度不可稱計。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119b0912" rend="inline">賢者阿難作禮
<lb n="1119b10" ed="T"/>白佛：「當何名斯經？<note n="1119031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔云何奉持〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔云何奉持〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119031"><lem wit="【大】">云何奉持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>？」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119b1012" rend="inline">佛言：「阿難！
<lb n="1119b11" ed="T"/>此經名為『法滅盡』，宣告一切宜令分別，功德
<lb n="1119b12" ed="T"/>無量不可稱計。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119b1207" rend="inline">四部弟子聞經，悲慘惆悵，皆
<lb n="1119b13" ed="T"/>發無上聖真道意，悉為佛作禮而去。</p>
<lb n="1119b14" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title>佛說法滅盡經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
